What is Amazon Aurora 


    Asynchronize Replica - 
    MySql and postgreSQL complitible RDS
    5 Times faster than any standard MYSQL and 3 times faster than postgreSQL
    Fully Managed by AWS RDS and which automate tasks such as: 
        Patching, backup ... all kind of admin tasks

    Self Healing
    Self Healing storage system which can scale upto 64TB/database instances 



    Service Username - Access credentials from the Admin
    Service Admin - FA
    IAM - Policy based - in terms what level of access does a user or company need